	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_SOCIALIST_REALISM_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Little Red Book</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_SOCIALIST_REALISM_HELP">
			<Text>Comrade-general, the other Ministers of War and I hold grave concerns over the allegiance of the young people. They have not struggled through the revolution as we have, they do not fully understand why we need Order.[NEWLINE]Comrade, what would you have us do?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_SOCIALIST_REALISM_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Leverage {1_YieldCost} to gain 3% Supply in every City and +5 XP on newly trained Units.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_SOCIALIST_REALISM_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Enter {4_Turns} of [ICON_RESISTANCE] Anarchy in order for [ICON_CULTURE] Boredom and [ICON_STRENGTH] Crime thresholds to permenantly be reduced by 5%.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_SOCIALIST_REALISM_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>All Cities lose 1 [ICON_CITIZEN] Population, but all eligible Units, as well as those constructed in the next {4_Turns}, gain the Drill II Promotion.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_SOCIALIST_REALISM_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>The answer is simple, comrades. National service for all.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_SOCIALIST_REALISM_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>If they have forgotten the revolution, the founders of our Ideology have given us the solution: have another!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_SOCIALIST_REALISM_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Manual labour, my dear general, is a remarkably effective lesson. Please, teach these uneducated youths.</Text>
		</Row>


